OL,3,CMan jailed after attacking woman with
OL,4,Cmeat cleaver in four hour ordeal
OL,6,FA man who attacked a woman with a meat
OL,7,Fcleaver in a four hour ordeal before
OL,8,Fforcing the woman to claim someone
OL,9,Felse had inflicted the injuries has
OL,10,Fbeen jailed for 21 years.
OL,12,FMark Nuttall tried to strangle his
OL,13,Fvictim with a rope before attacking
OL,14,Fher with a knife and a meat cleaver in
OL,15,Fhis house in Farnworth, Bolton, in
OL,16,FFebruary 2025.
