OL,3,CMan jailed after attacking woman with
OL,4,Cmeat cleaver in four hour ordeal
OL,6,FHe then forced the woman, suffered
OL,7,Fserious and life-changing injuries as
OL,8,Fa result of the attack, to lie to the
OL,9,Fpolice and say someone else had
OL,10,Fattacked her, but she told the truth
OL,11,Fto officers.
OL,13,FHe pleaded guilty to attempted murder
OL,14,Fin June 2025 and was sentenced at
OL,15,FBolton Crown Court on Monday 8
OL,16,FSeptember.
