OL,6,FDetective Constable Jon Liversage, of
OL,7,FBolton Criminal Investigation
OL,8,FDepartment, said: "The savagery of
OL,9,Fthis assault cannot be understated -
OL,10,Fthe bravery that the victim has shown
OL,11,Fthroughout the investigation is
OL,12,Finspiring and I want to thank her for
OL,13,Fassisting me throughout the
OL,14,Finvestigation.
OL,16,F"I hope this sentence can now give her
OL,17,Fand her family some closure.
