OL,4,Cmeat cleaver in four hour ordeal
OL,6,F"He kept her inside the address for
OL,7,Ffour hours and when he couldn't get
OL,8,Fhis own way, he attacked her with a
OL,9,Fmeat cleaver, hitting her in the head
OL,10,Ffour times causing life-changing
OL,11,Finjuries.
OL,13,F"Whilst she was bleeding heavily from
OL,14,Fher head, instead of getting her
OL,15,Fmedical attention, he mocked her.
